Tidak disangka dia sendiri tidak bisa mengendalikan mobilnya

265
00:10:25,399 --> 00:10:26,480
Dan jatuh

266
00:10:26,799 --> 00:10:27,759
Kita sudah tahu salah.

267
00:10:27,840 --> 00:10:28,879
Kelak tidak akan berani lagi.

268
00:10:28,919 --> 00:10:29,399
Benar.

269
00:10:30,240 --> 00:10:30,960
Semua salahnya

270
00:10:31,080 --> 00:10:32,360
Tidak ada hubungannya denganku.

271
00:10:32,600 --> 00:10:33,399
Dasar wanita.

272
00:10:33,600 --> 00:10:34,720
Bukankah kau juga mengejarnya?

273
00:10:34,759 --> 00:10:36,000
Aku mengejarmu dari belakang.

274
00:10:36,039 --> 00:10:38,159
Atau kau yang menyuruhku menghalanginya?

275
00:10:38,200 --> 00:10:39,360
Kau yang lari ke depan dengan sukarela.

276
00:10:39,399 --> 00:10:40,200
Kau yang mengusirnya.

277
00:10:40,240 --> 00:10:40,919
Lalu apa hubungannya denganku?

278
00:10:40,960 --> 00:10:41,679
Kau sekarang sudah membenciku. Ini...

279
00:10:41,799 --> 00:10:43,039
Sudah kubilang jangan kejar dia!

280
00:10:43,120 --> 00:10:43,600
Sudahlah.

281
00:10:44,919 --> 00:10:46,480
Kali ini aku hanya memberi kalian pelajaran.

282
00:10:47,440 --> 00:10:49,279
Lain kali tidak akan semudah itu.

283
00:10:49,759 --> 00:10:50,320
Ayo.

284
00:10:51,519 --> 00:10:51,879
Jangan pergi.

285
00:10:51,919 --> 00:10:52,440
Adik kecil.

286
00:10:53,039 --> 00:10:55,480
Jika kau pergi, bagaimana kita keluar?

287
00:10:55,720 --> 00:10:56,799
Tanganku terkubur di dalam.

288
00:10:56,840 --> 00:10:58,039
Biarkan kami keluar.

289
00:10:58,360 --> 00:10:58,879
Keluarkan kami!

290
00:10:59,279 --> 00:11:00,279
Lepaskan kami.

291
00:11:01,080 --> 00:11:02,200
Bukankah bisa bahasa daerah?

292
00:11:02,879 --> 00:11:04,279
Gali dirimu sendiri.

293
00:11:05,600 --> 00:11:06,000
Ayo.

294
00:11:07,320 --> 00:11:08,279
Selamatkan aku!

295
00:11:09,679 --> 00:11:11,159
Selamatkan aku!

296
00:11:14,559 --> 00:11:15,360
Gali.

297
00:11:17,399 --> 00:11:20,279
Tadi kau masih mengeluh

